<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.2.8">
<l>eppō tumpoṉmalariṭ ṭimaiyōrto ḻututaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>kaippō tukoṇṭiṟaiñcik kaḻalmēlva ṇaṅkaniṉṟāy</l>
<l>ippō teṉṉeñciṉuḷḷē pukuntāyaip pōkaloṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>naṟpō tuvaṇṭukiṇṭum naṟaiyūrniṉ ṟanampīyō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who stands while unblinking [celestials], praying, worshipping</l>
<l>with their bud-like hands [joined], bow at [your] anklets,</l>
<l rend="indent">always placing golden blossoms,</l>
<l>I cannot allow [your] going, you who have now entered into my heart,</l>
<l>O Noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr where bees burrow into fine buds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
